5000|$|Jeow bong (ແຈ່ວບອງ, แจ่วบอง; [...] ) is a {{sweet and}} spicy Lao chili paste made with Lao chilies, galangal and other {{ingredients}} {{commonly found in}} Laos. Its distinguishing ingredient, however, is water <b>buffalo</b> <b>skin.</b>|$|E
